Text:
To play with locked cards:
1. Install the game;
2. Copy from skidrow folder just the .exe (Dotp_d13) into the installation folder and replace;
3.Download and install SmartSteam (link from rapidshare worked for me)
4. Run SmartSteam and login (make an account if u have none);
5. Start the game from the desktop link.

Should work just fine, all except 3 decks are locked, 1 of the has no unlocked cards, other 2 have 30 unlocked cards. progress is saved (in unlock and campaign). The only thing that seems to not work properly are the achievements.
